This simulation is provided as a baseline to support comparison analysis
between the GRGM900C model and another lunar gravity model.

The simulation is not provided with any runs or verified data because we are
not verifying the LP150Q model.  However, it does have exactly the same
structure as the GRGM900C verification sim found in SIM_verif, so any input
files executed in SIM_verif can also be executed here to obtain the vehile
response to the LP150Q gravity model.
